<td align="center"><b>
<i>Epeolus minimus</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">&#40;Robertson, 1902&#41;</font></b><br>
<small><i>Triepeolus minimus </i>Robertson, 1902; <i>Argyroselenis minima </i>&#40;Robertson, 1902&#41;; <i>Argyroselenis minimus </i>&#40;Robertson, 1902&#41;; <i>Epeolus eastwoodae </i>Cockerell, 1937; <i>Epeolus beulahensis </i>Cockerell, 1904; <i>Epeolus lutzi </i>Cockerell, 1921; <i>Epeolus lutzi dimissus </i>Cockerell, 1921; <i>Epeolus arciferus </i>Cockerell, 1924; <i>Epeolus pilatei </i>Cockerell, 1924</small><p>
